    • Constructor Detail

      • WattDepotAdminClient

        public WattDepotAdminClient(String serverUri,
                    String username,
                    String orgId,
                    String password)
                     throws BadCredentialException
        Creates a new WattDepotAdminClient.
        Parameters:
        serverUri - The URI of the WattDepot server (e.g. "http://server.wattdepot.org/")
        username - The name of the user. The user must be defined in the WattDepot server.
        orgId - the id of the organization the user is in.
        password - The password for the user.
        Throws:
        BadCredentialException - If the user or password don't match the credentials on the WattDepot server.
